@Node "MO_SEGTRACKER" "PowerUP.guide/Main"
@Toc "Main"

Segtracker is an AmigaOS program which tracks hunks of loaded
programs so debugger tools can show which address belongs to which
program. Can be found in the Enforcer archive.

@EndNode
